Arnold Schwarzenegger &amp; Lewis Hamilton on Australia podium: I'll be back!
Lewis Hamilton shares a laugh with Arnold Schwarzenegger on the podium following theAustralian Grand Prixin Melbourne.The reigning world champion teases the Terminator, saying: "I thought you were taller," with Schwarzenegger responding: "I'm not wearing my high heels."The Hollywood actor was performing the post-race interviews on the podium at Albert Park, with Hamilton taking victory in the season-opening race.Available to UK users only.